data.description: Welcome to this great 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home. All rooms are spacious and offer great natural light. Kitchen with ceiling height cabinets and granite tops. Wood burning FP in cozy family room. Primary suite offers vaulted clg, walk-in closet and an en-suite bath. Good size back yard with 2 sheds that have a sub-panel for power. Great storage or future hang-out space. Extended driveway ensures great off-street parking. Newer shopping just outside of the community. Just 5 min to I-58 by-pass. Call for your private tour today!
